parameters:
\ncH-Haha! Thank you so much for appearing in our company's
advertisement today.

\ncBy the way, have the two of you known each other for a
while...?
\nc<>Ah, yes. We know each other very well.

\ncI-I see! Well, since the job is done, please take your time
and talk together.

\nc<>Wow, I never expected to meet Levantia-chan here. She's
been quite famous lately, right? Huh?

\nc<>I have no intention of talking to scum like you. Do whatever
you want here, I'm going home.

\nc<>Are you okay with that? If Levantia-chan goes home, I might
end up catching one of the employees here and chatting with
them, you know?

\nc<>I understand. Talk as much as you like. I can't guarantee
that I'll answer though.

\nc<>No, no, don't be so cold. This time it's a serious
conversation.

\nc<>To be blunt, here's the thing. I was wondering if we could
do another collaboration livestream together.

\nc<>Of course, not a secret livestream, but a regular
livestream.

\nc<>Well, I never expected you to have the audacity to ask for a
favor after doing something like that.

\nc<>That's harsh. I just actively tried to appeal to you
because I liked you.
\nc<>Please hit your head on a tofu corner and die.

\nc<>...So, why are you suddenly making such an offer? Your
livestreams don't really need it, do they?
\nc<>You're pretty popular right now. You're a bundle of talent.

\nc<>That's right! Look, you have a good-looking face and big
breasts. You're an unparalleled talent.

\nc<>I apologize... I'm looking forward to the next piece of bad
news.

\nc<>You seem grumpy, hey! Just so you know, it's not sexual
harassment, I'm serious.

\nc<>Do you have any idea how much effort I put into growing
this channel?

\nc<>What do you think? Since you're doing such dirty things
like secret livestreams, it'll probably be about six
months.
\nc<>The correct answer is less than three months!

\nc<>Of course, it's not just the power of secret livestreams.
It's because it hasn't even been a month since the
beginning.

\nc<>How about being honest and saying that you were surprised
when you were surprised?

\nc<>...Yes, that's right. It is indeed surprising. I also think
it's ridiculous.

\nc<>Appearance alone doesn't determine everything. It can't be
like that.

\nc<>If what you say is true, then why do attractive and
beautiful people in the world go through hardships?

\nc<>Well, someone like you might have never made any real
effort.

\nc<>Huh!? Why would it turn out like that!? Is it because
instead of cerebrospinal fluid, it's filled with semen!?

\nc<>There's no way there would be a man who stays silent after
being told something like that. Maybe it was you who had the
intention?

\nc<>Who would like such a thing...! A-And besides, my words have
a certain meaning...
\nc<>Obtained the memory M2: Advice from Senpai on Streaming.

The number of good listeners increased by 7,000, while the
number of bad listeners increased by 3,000.
